==English==
===Expression===
'''[[that]]'ll [[be]] the [[day]]!'''

#{{idiom}} Said in reply to something that one believes will never happen.
#:&ndash; ''I'm going to get into work on time today.''
#:&ndash; ''That'll be the day!''
